# 忽略根目录所有内容
/*

# 只保留这两个目录和 .gitignore 本身
!/ad-monitor/
!/docx/
!/.gitignore

# ad-monitor 内忽略敏感 / 运行时生成文件
ad-monitor/.env
ad-monitor/data.db
ad-monitor/data.db-shm
ad-monitor/data.db-wal
ad-monitor/**/__pycache__/
ad-monitor/**/*.pyc
ad-monitor/**/*.pyo
ad-monitor/.pytest_cache/
ad-monitor/CONVERSATION_LOG.md
